## Flutter-App (Repo-Root) — Legacy

Offline-First **Android-App** (Flutter/Dart), Material 3, Rot-Akzente.

### Tech-Stack

- **Flutter** ≥ 3.3, **provider** → `MedicationProvider`
- **DB:** sqflite → `DatabaseHelper.instance`
- **Scanner:** mobile_scanner

### Build

```powershell
cd C:\Users\afri8\Documents\emergency_meds
.\flutter_run.bat run
.\flutter_run.bat build apk
```

| Tool | Pfad |
|------|------|
| Flutter SDK 3.44.2 | `D:\Programme\Flutter\flutter` |
| Android SDK | `C:\Users\afri8\AppData\Local\Android\Sdk` |
| JAVA_HOME | `C:\Program Files\Android\Android Studio1\jbr` |

`flutter_run.bat` setzt `JAVA_HOME` und `ANDROID_HOME` automatisch.

### Flutter vs. PWA

Flutter hat einfacheres Schema (medications ohne Chargen-Modell v2, kein Backup/OCR/GS1 in gleichem Umfang). Neue Features primär in der PWA umsetzen.
